gurmukhi: ਗਨ ਗੰਧ੍ਰਬ ਦੋਖ ਦੋੳੂ ਹਰਖੇ || ਪੁਹਪਾਵਲਿ ਦੇਵ ਸਭੈ ਬਰਖੇ ||
transliteration: Gad Gaddhrab Dekh Dooo Harkhe|| Puhpaaval(i) Dev Sabhai Barkhe||
translation: The Ganas and Gandharvas, seeing both, were pleased and the gods showered flowers.

gurmukhi: ਮਿਲਿ ਗੇ ਭਟ ਅਾਪ ਬਿਖੈ ਦੋੳੂ ਯੋਂ || ਸਿਸ ਖੇਲਤ ਰੈਣ ਹੁਡੂ ਹੁਡ ਜਯੋਂ ||੧੮||
transliteration: Mil(i) Ge Bhat Aap Bikhai Dooo Yon|| Sis Khelat Rain Hudoo Hud Jyon||18||
translation: Two warriors were fighting with each other like the children competing with one another in their play during the night.18.

gurmukhi: ਰਣ ਧੀਰ ਬੀਰ ਸੁ ਗੱਜਹੀਂ || ਲਖਿ ਦੇਵ ਅਦੇਵ ਸੁਲੱਜਹੀਂ ||
transliteration: Ran Dheer Beer Su Gadj-heen|| Lakh(i) Dev Adev Sulajj-heen||
translation: The warriors are thundering in the war and seeing them both the gods and demons are feeling shy;

gurmukhi: ੲਿਕ ਸੂਰ ਘਾੲਿਲ ਘੂੰਮਹੀਂ || ਜਨ ਧੂਮ ਅਧੋ ਮੁਖ ਧੂਮਹੀਂ ||੧੯||
transliteration: Ik Soor Ghaail Ghoonm-heen|| Jan Dhoom Adho Moukh Dhoom-heen||19||
translation: The brave fighters, who have been wounded, are roaming and it appears that the smoke is flying upwards.19.

gurmukhi: ਭਟ ੲੇਕ ਅਨੇਕ ਪ੍ਰਕਾਰ ਹੀ || ਜੁੱਝੇ ਅਜੁੱਝ ਜੁਝਾਰ ਹੀ ||
transliteration: Bhat Ek Anek Prakaar Hee|| Jujjhe Ajujjh Jujhaar Hee||
translation: The brave fighters of many types are fighting bravely with one another.

gurmukhi: ਫਹਰੰਤ ਬੈਰਕ ਬਾਣਯੰ || ਠਹਰੰਤ ਜੋਧ ਕਿਕਾਣਯੰ ||੨੦||
transliteration: Phahrant Bairak Baanyan|| Thahrant Jodh Kikaanyan||20||
translation: The lances and arrows are being hurled and the horses of the warriors are advancing hesitantly.20.

gurmukhi: ਹਿਹਣਾਤ ਕੋਟ ਕਿਕਾਨ || ਬਰਖੰਤ ਸੇਲ ਜੁਅਾਨ ||
translation: Millions of horses are neighing and the warriors are showering arrows;

gurmukhi: ਛੁਟਕੰਤ ਸਾੲਿਕ ਸੁੱਧ || ਮਚਯੋ ਅਨੂਪਮ ਜੁੱਧ ||੨੧||
transliteration: Chhoutkant Saaik Suddh|| Machyo Anoopam Juddh||21||
translation: The bows have slipped and fallen from the hands and in this way the terrible and unique war is being waged.21.

gurmukhi: ਭਟ ੲੇਕ ਅਨਿਕ ਪ੍ਰਕਾਰ || ਜੁੱਝੇ ਅਨੰਤ ਸ੍ਵਾਰ ||
transliteration: Bhat Ek Anik Prakaar|| Jujjhe Anant Svaar||
translation: Many types of warriors and innumerable horsemen are fighting with one another;
